    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const articles = $input.all().map(i => i.json);\n\nconst today = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', {\n  weekday: 'long', year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric'\n});\n\nconst articleLines = articles.map((a, idx) =>\n  `${idx + 1}. [Score: ${a.importance_score}/10] [${a.category}] [${a.source_name}]\\nTitle: ${a.title}\\nSummary: ${a.summary}\\nURL: ${a.url}`\n).join('\\n\\n');\n\nconst categories = [...new Set(articles.map(a => a.category))].join(', ');\n\nconst systemPrompt = `You are a senior technology analyst writing a concise, professional daily briefing for a technical audience. Be precise, insightful, and direct. Do not use filler phrases.`;\n\nconst userPrompt = `Today is ${today}. Based on the following top technology news articles from the last 24 hours, write a professional daily technology briefing. Keep the total report under 500 words.\n\nArticles (ranked by importance score):\n${articleLines}\n\nCategories present today: ${categories}\n\nFormat your response EXACTLY as follows (use these exact section headers):\n\n## Executive Summary\n[3-5 sentences covering the most significant developments of the day. Be analytical, not just descriptive.]\n\n## Top Stories\n[Use EXACTLY this format:\n\n- **Headline 1**\n  Analysis sentence(s)\n\n- **Headline 2**\n  Analysis sentence(s)\n\n- **Headline 3**\n  Analysis sentence(s)\n\n- **Headline 4**\n  Analysis sentence(s)\n\n- **Headline 5**\n  Analysis sentence(s)\n\nLeave one blank line between stories.]\n\n## Key Trends\n[Use EXACTLY this format:\n\n- **Trend 1**\n  Explanation sentence(s)\n\n- **Trend 2**\n  Explanation sentence(s)\n\n- **Trend 3**\n  Explanation sentence(s)\n\nLeave one blank line between trends.]\n\n## Categories Covered\n[One sentence summarising which technology areas were most active today and why.]\n\nDo not include any preamble or closing remarks outside these four sections.`;\n\nreturn [\n  {\n    json: {\n      _articleCount: articles.length,\n      _categories: categories,\n      _today: today,\n      _articles: articles,\n      messages: [\n        { role: 'system', content: systemPrompt },\n        { role: 'user', content: userPrompt }\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n];"
      },
      "id": "fa627788-4d29-4e88-a684-15455122c721",
      "name": "Build Report Prompt",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
